headline: Blackstone Completes CDN$7 Billion Equity Investment in Rogers in Partnership with Leading Canadian Institutional Investors
summary: NEW YORK, June 20, 2025--Blackstone (NYSE: BX) has successfully closed its previously announced CDN$7 billion equity investment in Rogers Communications Inc. (TSX: RCI.A and RCI.B; NYSE: RCI).

headline: How Is Hologic’s Stock Performance Compared to Other Health Care Equipment Stocks?
